HHeretic - Port of ID Software's first person shooter game heretic
---------

This game requires the original heretic WAD files.  You can get the free
WAD file from http://www.dosgamers.com/downloads/wads/HERETIC1.zip.
Copy the HERETIC1.WAD into the !HHeretic folder.

See the !Run file in the !HHeretic folder for default runtime settings.
If music is too fast/slow try changing the '-samplerate 44100' option.
Valid values are 11025, 22050, 44100, 48000.
Add '-f' if you want to play fullscreen.
The screen resolution is fixed at 320x200.

This version created by the GCCSDK Autobuilder for details see:

http://www.riscos.info/index.php/GCCSDK#GCCSDK_Autobuilder

It also requires the SharedUnixLibrary which is available from:
http://www.riscos.info/downloads/gccsdk/sharedunixlib/system.zip

